title: I made a folder in my photos but now so can't find it
content: I'm going through an issue that I have taken pictures of and I moved them to a folder so they can stay together. The last thing I remember doing was naming it "Save file" and creating the album with the pictures I needed. Then, I went back into my photos and deleted the duplicate copies of them. Now I cannot find the "Save file" album or the pictures I needed from deleting the duplicates. But a bunch of other pictures I deleted are back onto the main camera file from when I deleted them.
